      <li>Sub-Zero 424 outdoor wine refrigerators (commercial use)</li>
      <li>Hoshizaki HR commercial wine reach-ins</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong></p>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li>New wine cellar construction (architect plus cellar builder trade)</li>
      <li>Wine cellar racking or carpentry</li>
      <li>Cellar electrical or lighting (unless refrigeration-integrated)</li>
      <li>Cellar humidification beyond integrated cooling-system humidifiers</li>
      <li>Pre-installation humidity assessments (this is wine cellar consultant trade)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 06 PRICING -->
<section class="section section-gray">
