    <h2 class="section-title">Wine cellar cooling repair costs in Southern California.</h2>

    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $120 (commercial tier), waived with repair. OEM parts on critical components (humidity modules, control boards, compressors). Written estimate before any work begins.</p>

