<!-- 07 WHY US -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why restaurants and hospitality call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Nine reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Wine Guardian + CellarPro expertise.</strong> These two brands cover roughly 70% of LA premium wine cellar installs. We carry common humidity modules and fan motors for both.</li>
      <li><strong>Multi-zone calibration knowledge.</strong> Restaurant cellars often have 3 to 4 separate temperature zones. Each requires individual thermostat service against zone-specific spec.</li>
      <li><strong>Humidity control awareness.</strong> Wine cellar isn't just temperature, humidity is equally critical for cork preservation. Most appliance shops don't understand this.</li>
